{"tid":1663564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好驚 油塘有手足係我面前比狗拉左","createTime":"2019-10-19T13:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T14:31:24.000Z","uid":303618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91d238b338eaae87c19d81de2c13abd6b1e03aec","tid":1663564,"uid":303618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"時間：20:5X 19/10/19<br />\n地點：油塘邨<br />\n<br />\n當時個男手足係XX樓樓下閘門位比1X隻狗夾住左 個手足一邊掙扎一邊講粗口屌撚班狗 比4-5個half-gear嘅夾左上狗車<br />\n<br />\n我淨係記得嘅2部狗車車牌 因為當時我好驚 有大量防暴+便衣mon撚住周圍 我記唔曬全部車牌號碼(起碼5部狗車 未計便衣私家車) 真係好對唔住果位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(唔記得左) AM6606 <br />\n(KT 1) AM7006</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足真係小心啲 啲狗拉人唔係人咁品 我親眼見過更加震撼⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e818354da3c0e5fabf336057f8370e794bdbdb4f","tid":1663564,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"b65a0b7d0dcb9b2103e4f02f6f108465717560b5","tid":1663564,"uid":158438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e134328da16479bd559b8f58d0dab9db6788cc0","tid":1663564,"uid":85691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4c6e21f5dac43182bd0d51c0896075cebb81535","tid":1663564,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37f638fa708cdc451eccc2a785968ba3bdf181be","tid":1663564,"uid":193877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a68860228d1d361741286d4960295d02404e2ac8","tid":1663564,"uid":44085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10